<h2>Why Choose Tiverton Water Polo Club?</h2>
<ul>
    <li>
        <strong>Passion for Polo:</strong> Our club is fuelled by a collective passion for water polo. From the splash 
        of the water to the thrill of competition, we embody the true spirit of the game.
    </li>
    <li>
        <strong>Inclusive Community:</strong> Everyone is welcome here. We foster a tight-knit community where teammates 
        become friends and mentors, creating bonds that extend beyond the pool.
    </li>
    <li>
